\c 1
\s Kurwara nokufa kwaAhazia
\s mambo weIsiraeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino vaMoabhu vakamukira vaIsiraeri, shure kwokufa kwaAhabhi.
\p
\v 2 Zvino Ahazia wakanga awira pasi napawindo yekamuri yake yokumusoro, yaiva paSamaria, akarwara akatuma nhume, akati kwavari, "Endai mundo- bvunza Bhaarizebhubhi, mwari weEki- roni, kana ndichapora pakurwara uku."
\v 3 Asi mutumwa waJehovha akati kuna Eria muTishibhi, "Simuka undosangana nenhume dzamambo weSamaria, uti kwavari, Asi hapana Mwari here pakati paIsiraeri, zvamondobvunza Bhaarizebhubhi, mwari weEkironi?'
\v 4 Naizvozvo zvanzi naJehovha, Haungaburukizve pamubhedha wawakwira, asi zvirokwazvo uchafa.' " Eria akabva.
\v 5 Ipapo nhume dzakadzokera kwaari, iye akati kwavari, "Madzokereiko?"
\p
\v 6 Ivo vakati kwaari, "Mumwe murume wakauya akasangana nesu, akati kwatiri, Endai, dzokerai kuna mambo wakakutumai, muti kwaari, Zvanzi naJehovha, asi hapana Mwari here pa- kati peIsiraeri, zvawotuma vanhu kundobvunza Bhaarizebhubhi mwari weEkironi? Naizvozvo haungaburukizve pamubhedha wawakwira, asi zvirokwa- zvo uchafa.'
\p
\v 7 "Akati kwavari, Murume, wakauya akasangana nemi, akakuudzai mashoko awo, wakanga akadiniko?' "
\v 8 Vakamupindura vakati, "Wakanga ari murume wakafuka nguo yemvere, akazvisunga chiuno chake nebhanire reganda." Iye akati, "Ndiye Eria muTishibhi."
\v 9 Ipapo mambo akatuma kwaari mukuru wavarume vana makumi mashanu, ana vanhu vake vana makumi mashanu. Iye akakwira kwaari, akamuwana agere pamu- soro pegomo. Akati kwaari, "Nhai munhu waMwari, zvanzi namambo, `Burukai.'
\p
\v 10 Eria akapindura, akati kumukuru wavana makumi mashanu, "Kana ndiri
\s munhu waMwati, moto ;aubmike kudenga, ukuparadze iwe navanhu vako vana makumi mashanu." Ipapo moto ukaburuka kudenga, ukamuparadza iye navanhu vake vana makumi mashanu.
\p
\v 11 Akatumazve kwaari mumwe mukuru wavana makumi mashanu. Iye aka- pindura, akati kwaari, "Nhai munhu waMwari, zvanzi namambo, Kurumidzai muburuke.' "
\v 12 Eria akapindura, akati kwavari, "Kana ndiri munhu waMwari, moto ngauburuke kudenga, ukuparadze iwe navanhu vako vana makumi mashanu." Ipapo moto waMwari ukaburuka kudenga, ukamuparadza iye navanhu vake vana makumi mashanu.
\p
\v 13 Akatumazve mumwe mukuru wavana makumi mashanu; wechitatu, anavanhu vake vana makumi mashanu. Zvino iye mukuru wavana makumi mashanu, wechitatu, akakwira, akapfugama namabvi ake pamberi paEria, akakumbira, akati kwaari, "Haiwa, munhu waMwari, upenyu hwangu nohwovaranda venyu ava vana makumi mashanu, ngachive chinhu chinokosha pamberi penyu.
\v 14 Tarirai, moto wakaburuka kudenga, ukapisa vakuru vaviri vavana makumi mashanu vokutanga navanhu vavo vana makumi mashanu; naizvozvo upenyu hwangu zvino ngachive chinhu chinokosha pamberi penyu."
\p
\v 15 Ipapo mutumwa waJehovha akati kuna Eria, "Buruka naye, usamutya hako." Akasimuka, akaenda naye kuna mambo.
\p
\v 16 Akati kwaari, "Zvanzi naJehovha, `Zvawakatuma nhume kundobvunza Bhaarizebhubhi, mwari weEkironi, asi hapana Mwari here pakati peIsiraeri, waungabvunza shoko rake? Naizvozvo haungaburukizve pamubhedha wawakwira, asi zvirokwazvo uchafa.'
\p
\v 17 Naizvozvo akafa seshoko raJehovha rakanga rarehwa naEria. Jehoramu akamutevera paushe, akatanga kubata ushe pagore rechipiri reJehoramu mwanakomana waJehoshafati mambo waJudha; nokuti iye wakanga asina mwana.
\v 18 Mamwe mabasa aAhazia aakabata, haana kunyorwa here mubhuku yamako- ronike amadzimambo aIsiraeri?
